\/forget-salat-sujud-al-sahwa\/","url_meta":{"origin":15536,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Prayer: When one forgets number of raka&#8217;at in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, prayed with us five cycles (raka'at). We said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, you added something to the prayer.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cWhat is that?\u201d They said, \u201cYou have prayed five cycles.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cVerily, I\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25393,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/11\/09\/what-unsure-how-much-prayed\/","url_meta":{"origin":15536,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salah: What if you forget how much you prayed?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 9, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf one of you doubts his prayer and does not know how much he has prayed, whether three or four cycles, then let him put aside his doubt and act upon what he is certain\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3964,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/01\/expiation-forget-to-pray\/","url_meta":{"origin":15536,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Expiation for forgetting to pray on time","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 1, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever forgets a prayer, let him pray it when he remembers. There is no expiation other than this.\u201d Then, the Prophet recited the verse, \"Perform prayer for My remembrance.\" (20:14) Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 597, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 684\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13728,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/25\/salat-restrain-yawnming\/","url_meta":{"origin":15536,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Prayer: Hold back yawning in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen one of you yawns in the prayer, let him restrain it as much as he can, lest Satan enter therein.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2995 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33026,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/01\/prophets-dua-ruku-sujud\/","url_meta":{"origin":15536,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Salat: The Prophet&#8217;s supplication in bowi